#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:30
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This &systemsettings; module allows you to configure which files should be "
"indexed for fast searching. It internally uses a technology called Baloo to "
"efficiently search through the files."
msgstr ""
"Ta modul &systemsettings; vam omogoča, da nastavite, katere datoteke naj se "
"indeksirajo za hitro iskanje. Za učinkovito interno iskanje po datotekah "
"uporablja tehnologijo Baloo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:37
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Add the widget <guilabel>Search</guilabel> to your panel or enable the "
"search in &krunner; to use the indexing results for faster access to your "
"documents."
msgstr ""
"Dodajte pripomoček <guilabel>Izvedi</guilabel> na ploščo ali omogočite "
"iskanje v &krunner; in uporabite rezultate indeksiranja za hitrejši dostop "
"do dokumentov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:41
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Activate the <guilabel>Enable File Search</guilabel> item if you want to use "
"desktop search capabilities in &dolphin; and other &kde; applications. "
"Uncheck the item if you do not want to use the file search with Baloo (it is "
"possible to use other search technologies, &eg; &kfind;)."
msgstr ""
"Če želite v aplikacijah &dolphin; in drugih aplikacijah &kde; uporabljati "
"možnosti iskanja na namizju, aktivirajte element <guilabel>Omogoči Iskanje "
"Datotek</guilabel>. Če ne želite uporabljati iskanja datotek s programom "
"Baloo, odstranite kljukico (lahko uporabite druge tehnologije iskanja, &eg; "
"&kfind;)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use <guilabel>Also index file content</guilabel> to also index the file "
"contents additional to the file names."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite <guilabel>Indeksiraj tudi vsebino datotek</guilabel>, če želite "
"poleg imen datotek indeksirati tudi njihovo vsebino."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check the <guilabel>Index hidden files and folders</guilabel> item to make "
"Baloo index the hidden files and folders."
msgstr ""
"Označite element <guilabel>Indeksiraj skrite datoteke in mape</guilabel>, če "
"želite, da Baloo indeksira skrite datoteke in mape."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:52
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Any file or folder name that starts with a period (<literal>.</literal>) is "
"hidden by default."
msgstr ""
"Vsako ime datoteke ali mape, ki se začne s piko (<literal>.</literal>), je "
"privzeto skrito."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:58
#, no-c-format
msgid "Folder specific configuration"
msgstr "Konfiguracija specifične mape"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:60
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You are presented with a list of folders that can be indexed. By default "
"only your entire <filename class=\"directory\"><envar>$HOME</envar></"
"filename> folder is indexed, and no other folders or drives are indexed."
msgstr ""
"Prikaže se seznam map, ki jih je mogoče indeksirati. Privzeto je indeksirana "
"samo celotna mapa <filename class=\"directory\"><envar>$HOME</envar></"
"filename>, druge mape ali pogoni pa niso indeksirani."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:65
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Removable media is never indexed by default. It can be explicitly removed "
"from the list of excluded folders and it will then be indexed."
msgstr ""
"Odstranljivi medij se privzeto nikoli ne indeksira. Lahko ga izrecno "
"odstranite s seznama izključenih map, nato bo indeksiran."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is possible to use the combo box next to each item in the list to "
"configure if it is <guimenuitem>Indexed</guimenuitem> or <guimenuitem>Not "
"indexed</guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"Z izbirnim poljem ob vsakem elementu na seznamu lahko nastavite, ali je "
"<guimenuitem>Indeksiran</guimenuitem> ali <guimenuitem>Neindeksiran</"
"guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use the trash button to remove an item from the list."
msgstr "Uporabite gumb za smeti, da odstranite element s seznama."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>Start indexing a folder...</guibutton>/<guibutton>Stop indexing a "
"folder...</guibutton>"
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>Začetek indeksiranja mape...</guibutton>/<guibutton>Zaključek "
"indeksiranja mape...</guibutton>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking any of the above-mentioned options displays the standard &plasma; "
"<guilabel>Select a folder to filter</guilabel> dialog and allows you to "
"choose the folder to be treated accordingly."
msgstr ""
"S klikom na katero koli od zgoraj navedenih možnosti se prikaže standardno "
"pogovorno okno &plasma; <guilabel>Izberite mapo za filtriranje</guilabel>, v "
"katerem lahko izberete mapo, ki bo ustrezno obdelana."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more info about additional configuration options &eg; how to add a drive "
"mounted outside your <filename class=\"directory\"><envar>$HOME</envar></"
"filename> folder please read <ulink url=\"https://community.kde.org/Baloo/"
"Configuration\">Baloo/Configuration</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Za več informacij o dodatnih možnostih konfiguracije &eg; kako dodati pogon, "
"nameščen zunaj mape <filename class=\"directory\"><envar>$HOME</envar></"
"filename>, preberite <ulink url=\"https://community.kde.org/Baloo/"
"Configuration\">Baloo/Configuration</ulink>."
